  <brief_title>Study of the Impact on the Evolution of the Disease in the Medium Term of the Implementation of a System of Extended Follow-up by Telephone Interview of Patients With an Eating Disorder Organized by the Nurses of the Eating Disorder Referral Center</brief_title>
